text.tspan: Tupu--nuku is the eldest of Matarikis daughters. She spends her time with
Papatnuku tending to plants. She pays special attention to making sure they have
everything they need to grow big and strong so they can produce kaikai food,
rongorongo medicine, and kkahukkahu clothing materials.
When we see her shining we are reminded that we all have our own special time and
